<item>
            <title>[LU-11006] lnetctl export creates &quot;peer&quot; root with no peer</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11006</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lnetctl export command creates a root entry in the YAML file for &quot;peer&quot; even when there are no peers.&lt;br/&gt;
This results in an erroneous return code from the function because of which &quot;systectl enable lnet&quot; or &quot;systemctl start lnet&quot; does not return successfully.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
